    <p class="pg-sub">Energy gummies have become the preferred fueling format for endurance athletes, replacing sticky gels and hard-to-digest bars. We tested 20 energy gummies across carbohydrate delivery, electrolyte content, GI tolerance, and real-world race performance to identify the 8 that keep you fueled from start to finish line.</p>
