    <p>GU Energy Labs has been the category leader in endurance nutrition since 1993, and their energy chews apply three decades of sports nutrition research to a gummy format. The dual-source carbohydrate blend (maltodextrin + fructose) utilizes separate intestinal transporters — SGLT1 for glucose and GLUT5 for fructose — enabling carbohydrate absorption rates up to 90g per hour when combined with additional fueling sources. The 450mg sodium per pack is the highest in this guide, specifically designed for athletes losing 800-1200mg sodium per hour through sweat during hot-weather endurance events.</p>

    <div class="tip-box">
