    <p>Clif Bloks are the most popular energy chew among recreational runners, and the cube-shaped format is no accident — each blok is designed to be popped into the mouth and chewed without breaking stride. The 24g of carbohydrates per pack from organic tapioca syrup provides a clean glucose source that most athletes tolerate well. The Margarita flavor deserves special mention: it delivers the highest sodium content (210mg) in the Bloks lineup, specifically formulated for hot-weather racing and heavy sweaters.</p>

